con:config.con:query: Select Top 10 a.shopper_id as a_shopper_id, a.brand_code as a_brand_code, a.login_user_name as a_login_user_name From shopper_LOGIN a Inner Join SHOPPER b On a.shopper_id = b.shopper_id Where a.reservation_user_id <> '' And b.logical_delete_flag = 0 And a.brand_code = 'R'

Select Top 10 a.shopper_id As a_shopper_id, a.brand_code As a_brand_code, a.login_user_name As a_login_user_name, a.login_password_text, b.shopper_first_name, b.shopper_last_name, a.creation_user_id, a.login_hint_question_text, a.creation_dtm From shopper_LOGIN a Inner Join SHOPPER b On a.shopper_id = b.shopper_id Where a.brand_code = '${DataSource#brand}' Order By a.creation_dtm Desc
